headline: Fastenal Company and RFK Racing Announce Body Guard Brand as Primary Focus of Partnership
summary: WINONA, Minn. & CONCORD, N.C., February 09, 2026--Fastenal Company (NASDAQ: FAST), a leading distributor of industrial and construction supplies, is launching a significant evolution to its partnership with RFK Racing. The iconic Fastenal blue paint scheme will be replaced with the striking black and orange colors of their Body Guard brand, aiming to increase awareness and engagement with this essential line of safety products.
